4/8/2026
Pushed DABLN 0.2 update

Changes:
- Allows user to input capitol D when inputting more than one die. 
- Previously "2D3" would throw an error. Has been fixed in 0.2

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4/10/2026
Pushed DABLN 0.3 update

Changes:
- Added Ability Modifiers and Ability Checks!
- At the start of the program, the user can input the 6 main ability modifiers (values from -5 to +5 only).
- The user can now respond to checks from the DM, where their ability modifiers are accounted 
for and are added/subtracted to the d20. 
- Retains basic dice rolling aspect

Roadmap going forward:
0.4:
Nat1 and Nat20 messages

0.5:
Temporary modifiers

0.6:
Saving throws

